<b-container>
  <b-row>
    <b-col sm="4" offset="4">
      <b-form @submit.prevent="login">
        <b-form-group
          id="input-group-1"
          label="Email address:"
          label-for="input-email"
          label-align="left"
          class="pb-1"
          ><b-form-input
            id="input-email"
            v-model="email"
            type="email"
            placeholder="Enter Email"
            required
          ></b-form-input>
        </b-form-group>

        <b-form-group
          id="input-group-2"
          label="Your Password:"
          label-for="input-password"
          label-align="left"
          class="pb-3"
          ><b-form-input
            id="input-password"
            v-model="password"
            placeholder="Enter Password"
            type="password"
            required
          ></b-form-input>
        </b-form-group>

        <b-button type="submit" block variant="primary">Login</b-button>
      </b-form>
      <hr />
      No Account yet?
      <router-link to="/register">Register Here</router-link>
    </b-col>
  </b-row>
</b-container>
